Detailed Description

cvmx_cpri::_map_tbl_index

This register specifies which mapping table segment will be read/written by accesses to any of the registers: * CPRI()_MAP_TBL_RX0 * CPRI()_MAP_TBL_RX1 * CPRI()_MAP_TBL_TX0 * CPRI()_MAP_TBL_TX1

Note that a write to CPRI()_MAP_TBL_RX1 or CPRI()_MAP_TBL_TX1 will automatically increment this register to one.
